profile:
We are an award winning moving company that has been providing high quality relocation services for commercial, industrial and residential relocation services for customers in Kingston for several years. We are the local movers they know they can depend on to do the job quickly and efficiently. Kingston residents and business people have long praised us for being the best movers in the Limestone city. We have a highly skilled, experienced staff, affordable prices, excellent customer service, vast knowledge of the most efficient routes in Kingston, as well as free moving insurance.

Superior Staff
Our movers are specially trained and know how to handle delicate, sensitive, housewares, electrical equipment and machines. They are prompt, courteous, polite, friendly, knowledgeable and professional. Our movers undergo thorough background checks and are licensed, bonded and insured. They will ensure your things are properly packed, protected and loaded to ensure they get to your new location in Kingston or anywhere else safely. Our staff is committed to the highest customer service standards and willing to go the extra mile to make sure that the customer is satisfied.

profile:
Voted Kingston Ontario's #1 moving and storage company year after year.
Frank’s Worldwide Moving is a family owned mid-sized company established in 1989, we are large enough to handle all your moving, storage, and warehousing needs and small enough that you do not get lost in the bureaucracy. We are fully licensed and insured.
We have well trained and well informed people working in all aspects of our business, from the gentleman who answers the phone, to the movers who load your truck.

The person who answers the phone is able to answer most of your questions. No more waiting for your important questions to be answered.
Most estimates can be written on the spot. There is no more waiting for the sales people to get back to you.
Our companies philosophy is to treat people like we want to be treated ourselves.

We are a full service mover. Make the right move, call Frank’s Worldwide Moving.
